					<sentence id="S5.149">(BD???) D-mib (green in B, B?, C, C?, D, and D?) co-localized with Ser (red in [B and B??]), Dl (red in [C and C??]), N (red in [D and D??]), and E-Cadherin (E-Cad; blue in [D and D???]) and was found apical to Discs-large (Dlg; blue in [B, B???, C, and C???]) in notum cells located at the edges of the wing discs.</sentence>
					<sentence id="S5.150">(EE??) D-mib (green in [E and E?]) co-localized with Dl (red in [E and E??]) at the apical cortex of wing pouch cells.</sentence>
